sequenceDiagram
  participant Proposer as Signer P (in quorum)
  participant CoSigner as Signer Q (in quorum)
  participant Server
  participant Entity

  Note over Proposer,Entity: Entity status = Idle<br/>Entity.mempool ≠ ∅
  
  Proposer->>Server: add_tx
  Server-->>Entity: tx appended
  
  Proposer->>Server: propose_block(hash, txs)
  Server-->>Entity: status → Proposed approves ← {P}outbox = broadcast to ALL signers
  
  Server-->>CoSigner: Outbox propose_block
  Note over CoSigner: Receives proposal,<br/>immediately approves it
  
  CoSigner->>Server: approve_block(hash, from=Q)
  Note over CoSigner: Sends approval to ALL signers<br/>including proposer
  Server-->>Entity: approves ∪= {Q} if 2/3 reached → enqueue commit_block to proposer
  
  Server-->>Proposer: Outbox commit_block
  
  Proposer->>Server: commit_block(hash)
  Server-->>Entity: apply txs status → Idle height +1 generate transfer msgs
  
  Note over Server,Entity: transfer msgs routed<br/>as new ServerTx→mempool
